# Keep the docker build context lean — these are never needed inside an image
# build (a from-source Dockerfile only needs source + Cargo manifests/lock).
# Patterns must match nested paths too (a monorepo has many target/ dirs), so
# use **/ forms — a bare `target/` only matches the context root.
target/
**/target/
target-linux/
**/target-linux/
.git/
.vat/
**/.vat/
**/node_modules/
**/*.log
pkg/
**/*.png
